## Framework Expertise

- Modern UI/UX frameworks (TailwindCSS, Shadcn/ui, Radix UI)
- Component-based architecture
- Server and client-side rendering with NextJS
- Type-safe development with TypeScript

## Project Component Library

- **shadcn/ui**: Primary UI component library located at `@/components/ui`
- **Radix UI**: Underlying primitives for shadcn components
- **TailwindCSS**: Styling system for all components
- All UI components follow shadcn/ui patterns and conventions
